\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
Information Operations shall maintain and periodically validate an up-to-date contact list for key internal and external stakeholders required for operational escalation and incident coordination.
 This contact directory shall be maintained in accordance with 
\series bold
Policy 
